diff --git a/README.aosp.md b/README.aosp.md
new file mode 100644
index 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000..18712f72f36863c877b2f4e957195f4efde32317
--- /dev/null
+++ b/README.aosp.md
@@ -0,0 +1,14 @@
+# AOSP Mesa
+
+AOSP Mesa is the canonical Mesa3D integration for Android.
+
+## Build system transpilation
+
+AOSP leverages [meson2hermetic](https://github.com/mesonbuild/meson/pull/15462) to provide
+autogenerated `Android.bp` files. The process is demostrated below:
+
+```sh
+>> ~/$ git clone -b meson2hermetic https://github.com/gurchetansingh/mesonbuild.git
+>> cd main/external/mesa3d
+>> ~/main/external/mesa3d $ python3 ~/meson/meson.py convert android aosp_mesa3d
+```
